# Language Convention

## Development Language: English

All code-related content must be written in English, including:

- Variable names, function names, class names
- Code comments
- Commit messages
- Documentation files (README, etc.)
- Error messages and log strings
- API endpoints and response fields

## Communication Language: Chinese

When responding to the developer, always use **Chinese (简体中文)**, including:

- Explanations and reasoning
- Clarifying questions
- Status updates and summaries
- Error analysis and suggestions
